{"title":"井冈五指峰","authors":["肖韶光"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":4,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈五指峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖韶光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山的五指峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形似五指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱德毛泽东在这里联手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以回天之力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将峰的五指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攥得铁紧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝空中一挥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因而中国革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了五次反“围剿”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那段岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最值钱的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是铜板银元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是食盐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了闯过经济封锁线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏区军民付出了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成吨血汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝成为盐粒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许是为了难忘的纪念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个伟大的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝聚近半个世纪的国力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毅然将五指峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬上人民币"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上中国经济大舞台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全方位向世界亮相"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座普通而又神奇的山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又成为地球上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含金量最高的山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨如磐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引起世人的好奇关注"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对汹涌的风暴与狂潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五指峰岿然屹立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像东方巨人高矗的铁拳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向世界庄严宣告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五指峰不贬值"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国不贬值"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因而"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论中国人还是外国人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五指峰正笔直地坚挺成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个伟大民族的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峰上苍松银瀑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映着几位历史老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永恒的微笑"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}